:JOURNEY
Reading Columbine
Section
Impact
- Day of the shooting | 4 | Unsensationalized | Specific and accurate without exploitation
- Psychological chapters | 5 | Most important | Hardest to accept and most necessary
- Myth-busting | 5 | Each correction lands | Every corrected myth makes the truth darker
- Survivor chapters | 5 | Most moving | The most necessary sections in the book

:NOTE
This book should be read by anyone who thinks they know what happened at Columbine. \
The myths are so embedded in the story that even people who followed it closely hold them.

